Deutsch: Plugin Update auf die Minecraft Version 1.18
English: Updated the Plugin for the Minecraft Version 1.18

At this Time this Version is available, you all can have the EVENT-PREMIUM-KEY without me giving it to you.
At the Moment no Premium Features are available, but soon there will come some.
The Download for this Version is available until 01.01.2022 or I forgot to upload a new version then it's no longer aviable.

New Features:
GlobalMute -> With /globalmute; /chatmute or /mutechat you can disable the chat for everyone that don't have the Permission "yvtils.ba.bypass.mutechat".
AFKDamageKick -> With /afkdamage you can toggle the automatic kick when you get Damage, but you don't allowed to move to much otherwise you will get kicked and the Setting will disabled. When you get Damage you will get kicked and the Setting get disabled. -> Required Permission: "yvtils.ba.command.afkdamage"
Config has new Options. -> Version 8

Version 4.6.6
Status Module: Set your own Status or select one of the default, you can customize the Default Status in the Config System.
Language System: The Language System is now on the Way, I want to have good translations, so you can help to translate on a website. (Link will come with full release)
Mainteance Feature: This Feature is now finished and work now how I want that it work.
From now on every new Feature become a Version Tag and since when it is in the Plugin.

Version 4.6.6
Language System 68% finished - Process continues the latest on 18.06.2022

Full Changelog Version 4.6.6:
Updated for Version 1.19
Status Module → Set your own Status or selected of one of the default Status which can be set by the Server Owner.
Maintenance System is now fixed and finished and should work.
Plugin has now an own Language System with the Languages German and English, with your help there will come more. Customize 99% of the Plugin Messages
Removed the AFKKickOnDamage and Custom Crafting Recipes (CCR) CCR will come back in the Version 4.6.7 with a better Version and an own GUI
Commands like Heal or GM (Gamemode) will also be usable on other Players when Version 4.6.7 comes out.
4.6.7 Alpha 1: Updated CCR Added Sit Function Optimized Code

« Version 4.6.7.b1 Changelog »
Download: https://yvnetwork.de/download/325/ ||The Download is maybe brocken, my web Server doesn't really work in the moment.||
» CCR - CustomCraftingRecipes First Version is coming with **two** crafting recipes! Open the GUI with '/ccr' and craft you an invisible Item-Frame, or an Light-Block Tutorials for the Recipes are on **GitHub** *soon available*!
» Sit Added ability to sit Use /sit or click on a stair
» Language System Rework 2.0 Files don't need to be deleted when new Strings are getting added, with new Versions.
» Status Module Added Messages for better overview In example: Status set Message, Status Clear Message
» Command Usage Most Commands like /fly; /gm can now be used on other Players.
» Update Announcer The Update Announcer now works for every Plattform. Maybe doesn't work on Direct Server Hosters like Nitrado, gPortal, Aternos. They maybe block the accecs to the Database. Please report any bugs with this.
» Bug Fixes
» And some other things
«================================»
Please report any bugs on the Discord (https://yvnetwork.de/yvtils-smp/support) or per Private Message to @WolfiiYV#3204. The Full Release is **coming soon**! (1 - 7 Days)
(Copied from Discord)
